asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

Chester joined the resistance against the zombie apocalypse in his early years where he fought side by side with his squad and girlfriend, Bunnifer Lopez. They grew up together and have vague memories of their parents who died early on in their lives due to a widespread virus named Carrotavirus. Chester and Bunnifer split up years ago when a group of zombies attacked the camp they were stationed in and have never made contact with each other since. Later that same year the zombie clan were largely defeated and the war had ended. Chester moved to the coast to pursue his ambitions in music where he was propelled to success with his band. He rocks a facemask to honour his parents, he wears a chain around his neck with the emblem of the resistance on it, the peace symbol, and the print on his vest is to remember his love and fellow comrades who passed away or disappeared during the last war against the zombies. He has a gut feeling that Bunnifer is still out there and that he will reunite with her one day. As of recent, there have been rumours that the zombies are secretly preparing for another war and members of the resistance have made contact with Chester.  One More Light RIP.

description: I'm literally shaking right now, I received a notification that I bought the fluf and my money is gone but everything is crossed out .. I dont know what to do. I moved all the way from Australia to the USA so I could have the best connection when getting one of these prized flufs. Ive been studying Youtube videos every night for 3 weeks straight. I cant even sleep without dreaming about fluf.  Im scared. Can you please help me. Im literally shaking so bad right now.  Fluffy Business where are you. Please Fluffy Business . My son is crying in the other room and I cant speak to him. He looked at me and said "Father, why does the backend not hold up that well?" and he's only 2 years old.. I cant look that kid in the face and tell him I lost my fluf.. Im begging you . I skipped out on leg day for this... I'm literally shaking rn
